OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFirms urged to cut down on 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Falcohol at work parties    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Businesses are being urged to limit the
OL,6, amount of alcohol served at work social
OL,7, events in order to prevent people from 
OL,8, acting inappropriately towards others. 
OL,10,FThe warning from the Chartered         
OL,11,FManagement Institute (CMI) comes as it 
OL,12,Freleases a new poll, suggesting a third
OL,13,Fof managers have seen harassment or    
OL,14,Finappropriate behaviour at parties.    
OL,16,FWomen were more likely than men to say 
OL,17,Fthey had witnessed this behaviour.     
OL,19,FThe CMI's boss said alcohol "doesn't   
OL,20,Fneed to be the main event" at parties. 
